Alright, hop in.

04:16.824 --> 04:18.690
How you doing tonight?

04:18.692 --> 04:20.692
I'm excellent,
how about yourself?

04:20.694 --> 04:22.862
Not bad, about to get off.

04:22.863 --> 04:25.366
Yeah, good for you.

04:26.634 --> 04:28.235
My night's just getting started.

04:30.571 --> 04:31.672
So where you headed?

04:33.907 --> 04:36.443
Straight to Hell along
with everybody else.

04:40.047 --> 04:40.881
I'm sorry?

04:42.049 --> 04:46.353
But first, how about
235 Detroit Street?

04:46.354 --> 04:47.187
Okay, alright.

05:15.182 --> 05:18.017
It says you have a
five star Ryde rating.

05:18.018 --> 05:20.220
Yeah, request the
best, that's what I say.

05:21.489 --> 05:23.423
You been doing this awhile?

05:23.424 --> 05:24.625
Yeah, a couple months.

05:25.559 --> 05:26.460
Pretty good gig?

05:27.895 --> 05:28.729
Ah, it's alright.

05:29.730 --> 05:31.230
You're full time?

05:31.231 --> 05:33.132
Nah, just after the day job.

05:33.133 --> 05:34.334
Keeps me out of trouble.

05:37.905 --> 05:40.673
You ever have a
really bad passenger?

05:40.674 --> 05:42.375
Nah, most of 'em
are pretty chill.

05:42.376 --> 05:43.810
Really?

05:43.811 --> 05:45.912
Come on.
No, seriously.

05:45.913 --> 05:49.082
That's cop-out, seriously,
your worse passenger?

05:50.283 --> 05:52.419
Hmm, my worst passenger.

05:52.420 --> 05:56.022
Absolute worst passenger ever?

05:56.023 --> 05:57.057
My worst passenger.

05:58.191 --> 06:00.059
Hmm, let me think.

06:00.060 --> 06:03.596
Okay, alright, so,
a few weeks ago,

06:03.597 --> 06:06.133
I'm driving this dude and
this girl to a concert,

06:07.568 --> 06:10.537
and both of 'em is as drunk
as a skunk and high as a kite.

06:10.538 --> 06:13.339
Halfway there, he realizes he
forgot his phone back at home,

06:13.340 --> 06:15.908
and you know, his phone
had his tickets on it.

06:15.909 --> 06:18.811
Anyway, this dude he's just
flipped out on this girl,

06:18.812 --> 06:20.580
sayin' that she was
supposed to remind him

06:20.581 --> 06:22.214
about the tickets
and everything,

06:22.215 --> 06:23.816
and then he just
like raised his hand

06:23.817 --> 06:24.851
like he was gonna hit her.

06:24.852 --> 06:26.085
Did he?

06:26.086 --> 06:27.319
No, he didn't hit her,

06:27.320 --> 06:28.488
but you could tell that
he had done it before

06:28.489 --> 06:29.956
by the way that she flinched,

06:29.957 --> 06:31.758
and then I just told him
to calm the hell down,

06:31.759 --> 06:33.426
and then he started
threatening me.

06:33.427 --> 06:34.827
So what you do?

06:34.828 --> 06:36.596
I told him that if
he didn't calm down

06:36.597 --> 06:38.731
I was gonna call the cops.

06:38.732 --> 06:40.500
So I turned around and
drove him back home.

06:40.501 --> 06:43.035
He was pouting and
shit and complaining,

06:43.036 --> 06:44.236
and then he got his and phone,

06:44.237 --> 06:46.138
then I drove 'em
back to the concert.

06:46.139 --> 06:47.373
I didn't even charge them

06:47.374 --> 06:49.108
for the extra time
and the mileage,

06:49.109 --> 06:50.677
and then had the nerve
to call corporate

06:50.678 --> 06:51.744
and give me a zero rating.

06:51.745 --> 06:52.979
Can you believe that?

06:52.980 --> 06:54.313
You should have kicked his ass.

06:54.314 --> 06:55.348
Yeah, you're right.

06:56.717 --> 06:59.118
No, I'm serious.

06:59.119 --> 07:01.921
