hand on a woman like that

07:01.922 --> 07:03.956
deserves to be punished.

07:03.957 --> 07:05.157
But he didn't
actually touch her.

07:05.158 --> 07:06.093
Yeah, but you
said you could tell

07:06.094 --> 07:07.894
he'd done it before, right?

07:07.895 --> 07:08.829
Well that was my
impression, yeah.

07:08.830 --> 07:10.563
Do you trust your instincts?

07:10.564 --> 07:11.664
Usually.

07:11.665 --> 07:13.500
And he threatened you?

07:13.501 --> 07:14.934
Yeah.

07:14.935 --> 07:17.004
You should have
broke his fucking nose.

07:18.639 --> 07:20.673
I mean it, seriously.

07:20.674 --> 07:23.543
If I was back here with a girl
that I was clearly abusing,

07:23.544 --> 07:25.478
and you spoke up for her
and I threatened you,

07:25.479 --> 07:26.379
what would you do?

07:28.315 --> 07:29.149
Huh?

07:30.417 --> 07:31.984
Well with all due respect,

07:31.985 --> 07:33.587
I would break your fucking nose.

07:35.856 --> 07:37.256
Now that's what
I'm talking about.

07:40.360 --> 07:41.861
Ah, fuck.

07:41.862 --> 07:42.896
Is everything okay?

07:43.897 --> 07:44.732
Ah, my phone.

07:46.199 --> 07:47.535
Well, you wanna use mine?

07:48.602 --> 07:49.836
Could I?

07:49.837 --> 07:50.671
Yeah, sure.

07:52.706 --> 07:54.440
Thanks, I appreciate it.

07:54.441 --> 07:56.544
Yeah, don't mention it.

08:00.480 --> 08:01.381
It's Thomas.

08:02.583 --> 08:05.051
No, I have good news.

08:05.052 --> 08:07.154
Mr. Richardson
agreed to your terms.

08:08.255 --> 08:10.223
Yes, in fact, he already has.

08:12.292 --> 08:14.260
I have it right with me.

08:14.261 --> 08:16.964
You gonna be around for
awhile, I mean, I'm on my way.

08:18.899 --> 08:19.733
Yes.

08:20.734 --> 08:21.569
You're welcome.

08:26.073 --> 08:27.506
I really appreciate it.

08:27.507 --> 08:28.709
Yeah, no problem, man.

08:48.095 --> 08:50.197
By the way, your
numbers don't add up.

08:51.298 --> 08:52.099
I'm sorry?

08:53.567 --> 08:56.936
You said you'd been working
for two months, give or take?

08:56.937 --> 08:59.505
Yeah, a couple
months, give or take.

08:59.506 --> 09:00.807
Hell, let's call it 10 weeks

09:00.808 --> 09:05.779
and two or three days a
week, let's say three.

09:06.513 --> 09:08.581
What, 10 fares a night?

09:08.582 --> 09:11.050
On average, yeah,
that's about right.

09:11.051 --> 09:16.056
That's a total of 300
fares in 10 weeks, liberally?

09:16.624 --> 09:18.257
Okay.

09:18.258 --> 09:23.096
Well, Ryde does its calculations
on tenths of percentages.

09:24.732 --> 09:28.434
So even with one zero rating,

09:28.435 --> 09:32.271
you would need no
less than 2,000 fares,

09:32.272 --> 09:37.277
1,999 of them,
five star ratings,

09:38.445 --> 09:39.579
just to average out
to a five star rating.

09:40.480 --> 09:42.248
Yeah, so?

09:42.249 --> 09:44.217
So that's
statistically impossible

09:45.285 --> 09:46.986
unless you're
tweaking the numbers.

09:46.987 --> 09:49.689
Hey, look, I just drive the car.

09:49.690 --> 09:50.923
Are you?

09:50.924 --> 09:52.725
I don't know what
you're talking about.

09:52.726 --> 09:53.761
Dude, it's okay.

09:54.995 --> 09:56.195
Seriously.

09:56.196 --> 09:57.864
It's none of my business.

09:57.865 --> 09:59.598
If anything, I'm impressed.

09:59.599 --> 10:00.700
I wouldn't have the first clue

10:00.701 --> 10:02.101
how to mess with their system.

10:02.102 --> 10:04.336
Look, man, I'm just
trying to make a living.

10:04.337 --> 10:06.906
I'm serious, no worries.

10:06.907 --> 10:09.476
It's not the worst thing
anyone's ever done, right?

10:10.577 --> 10:12.545
I mean, you're
obviously a good driver.

10:20.954 --> 10:23.322
So what's the worst
thing you've ever done?

10:25.659 --> 10:26.493
We're here.

10:32.532 --> 10:34.000
Shit.

10:34.001 --> 10:35.535
The gate code is 4247#.

10:55.055 --> 10:56.790
And make a left here.

11:02.562 --> 11:03.396
It's that one.

11:05.098 --> 11:05.933
Straight up.

11:12.205 --> 11:14.841
Well, Mr. Thomas, it's
been an interesting evening.

11:14.842 --> 11:17.077
Well, I'm gonna
need a ride back.

11:18.445 --> 11:22.782
I'm sorry, did you have
plans or something?

11:22.783 --> 11:23.983
Ah, actually...

11:23.984 --> 11:26.118
Shit, man, you
should have told me.

11:26.119 --> 11:27.486
I thought I did.

11:27.487 --> 11:30.490
Shit, man, now I feel terrible.

11:31.725 --> 11:35.527
Look, it'll only
take a minute, okay?

11:35.528 --> 11:37.229
I promise.

11:37.230 --> 11:39.465
And then you can just drop
me off on the way back.

11:39.466 --> 11:41.601
It's probably right
on your way anyway.

11:42.803 --> 11:45.237
Yeah, no worries, man.

11:45.238 --> 11:47.007
I'll even tip ya
extra, I promise.

11:48.441 --> 11:50.343
Just give me a sec, I
gotta get organized here.

11:53.413 --> 11:55.281
Can you hold this for a sec?

11:55.282 --> 11:56.249
Yeah.

12:00.387 --> 12:01.188
Nice pen.

12:02.055 --> 12:03.289
You like it?

12:03.290 --> 12:04.423
Yeah.

12:04.424 --> 12:05.692
It's a retirement gift.

12:09.662 --> 12:13.732
Alright, I'll be back
in two minutes, tops.

12:13.733 --> 12:15.634
Alright, I'll be here.

12:15.635 --> 12:16.904
Alright, I'll be right back.

12:37.490 --> 12:38.325
